<span id="freeTextContainer6760119764318499695">Well, I&apos;m going to be completely honest and just say that this book was pretty boring. It dragged on, and she kept repeating the same concept of the story, over and over! &quot;yes, I get it, now move on with the story!&quot; I know a lot of people like her books, and for me it&apos;s a toss up, some I like, and some I don&apos;t. Unfortunatly, this is one I did not. I found my mind wandering to other things, and the characters really bothered me. Once again, she&apos;s very repeditive when it comes to the story line, s</span>
  <span id="freeText6760119764318499695" style="display:none">Well, I'm going to be completely honest and just say that this book was pretty boring. It dragged on, and she kept repeating the same concept of the story, over and over! "yes, I get it, now move on with the story!" I know a lot of people like her books, and for me it's a toss up, some I like, and some I don't. Unfortunatly, this is one I did not. I found my mind wandering to other things, and the characters really bothered me. Once again, she's very repeditive when it comes to the story line, some people like that, but for me, just give it to me once and I'm good. Needless to say, this book was one of a trilogy, and I won't be getting book 2.</span>
